index_terms: CHICAGO MILWAUKEE ST. PAUL PACIFIC RAILROAD
summary: AN ORDINANCE terminating the interest of the Chicago, Milwaukee, St. Paul and Pacific Railway Company in franchises granted by Ordinances 13633, 102809, and 102810, each as amended and supplemented from time to time, and declaring expired and of no further effect the franchises granted by Ordinances 14532, 17330, 20094, 20095, 21594, and 21656.
